name: Ep. 116 - The Expanse S6E6 Part 2 + Special Guests Daniel & Naren
summary: Ty Franck (one half of James S.A. Corey) and Wes Chatham ('Amos Burton' on The Expanse) are joined by none other than Daniel Abraham and Naren Shankar to discuss their favorite Expanse episodes and favorite series finales.
